WEBVTT

00:00:01.375 --> 00:00:02.976
I'm a human rights lawyer.

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:05.518
I've been a human rights
lawyer for 30 years,

00:00:05.542 --> 00:00:07.417
and this is what I know.

00:00:09.125 --> 00:00:12.708
Once there was a man alone in a room.

00:00:13.625 --> 00:00:15.792
And his name was Alton.

00:00:17.250 --> 00:00:19.976
And then seven other men, seven strangers,

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:23.726
rushed into his room and dragged him out.

00:00:23.750 --> 00:00:28.101
And they held him
in a horizontal, crucifix position.

00:00:28.125 --> 00:00:30.059
One on each arm,